de.systemagmbh.common.math
Class CSysInterval

java.lang.Object
  de.systemagmbh.common.math.CSysInterval
Deprecated. As of release 2.5, replaced by de.systemagmbh.tools.math.CSysInterval

public class CSysInterval
extends Object

This class is a wrapper for numeric Intervals. In the class MathTool you will see some methods requiring Intervals as argument. Some functions in the class Statistics return Intervals as result. CSysInterval is a simple class, but really useful.
